## Scope

```
infra/                    production IaC apply
scripts/seed-prod.ts      production-only seed
docs/runbooks/            go-live procedures
.github/workflows/        prod deploy workflow (human-gated)
```

### Files NOT touched

- New MVP features (scope frozen)
- Non-prod synthetic seed on production

## Constraints

### Use

- `Docs/09` release checklist every prod step
- Four-eyes approval production apply
- Env-specific config explicit (not staging copy-paste)
- Prod seed script separate from dev seed
- Sentetik veri UAT only
- RDS snapshot before go-live

### Avoid

- Agent "just deploy prod" without checklist
- Dev seed on production
- Real ethics data in UAT notes/bugs
- Skip UAT sign-off
- Full rollout before pilot monitor window

