- [ ] UAT checklist executed (sentetik veri)
- [ ] Blocker/critical bugs closed
- [ ] UAT sign-off: Etik + KVKK + Bilgi Güvenliği
- [ ] RDS pre-go-live snapshot taken
- [ ] Email deliverability test (SPF/DKIM/DMARC)
- [ ] Pilot group cases processing
- [ ] Full rollout + on-call rotation
- [ ] Human Gate complete — **MVP live**

### Manual smoke test

```bash
# Prod smoke (human-supervised)
# 1. Superadmin OIDC login + MFA enroll
# 2. Sentetik report → case → task flow pilot tenant
# 3. CloudWatch: error rate, 5xx, login rate dashboards
```

## Explicit Don'ts

- Prod deploy without checklist + human approval
- Staging config blind copy to prod
- Dev/non-prod seed on production
- Real ethics data in non-prod UAT
- Skip RDS pre-launch snapshot
- Agent-only go-live decision
- `main`'e direct push

## Kısıtlar & Riskler

| Risk | Önlem |
| --- | --- |
| Agent prod deploy unsupervised | Human gate every apply; four-eyes |
| Agent runs dev seed on prod | prod seed guard + separate script |
| UAT bug avalanche | İterasyon 4 priority triage; defer medium/low |
| Env config drift | Explicit prod tfvars checklist İterasyon 1 |

